highlights.text: Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Beautiful People (feat. Khalid)” is the highest at #5.
“Hot Girl Summer (feat. Nicki Minaj & Ty Dolla $ign)” by Megan Thee Stallion, Ty Dolla $ign, and Nicki Minaj is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #32.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 136 weeks straight.
“Love Me” by Lil Tecca is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 75 spots at #95.
